room_title: Escape room "Retro" by Urban Enigmas in Athens
room_address: 10 Huntington Road Unit B70 Athens, GA 30606
room_description: Let “Retro” take you back to the good old days of fun and games. Forget what you know about escape rooms and try your hands at Athens’ first true puzzle room, where it’s not about how fast you get out, but how many points you get out with. Where will you fall on the leaderboard?
